  <title>nerdtree 自动切换到当前目录</title>
  <link>https://williamlfang.github.io/2022-09-13-nerdtree-%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E5%88%87%E6%8D%A2%E5%88%B0%E5%BD%93%E5%89%8D%E7%9B%AE%E5%BD%95/</link>
